subject: Customise the DbusObject paths as per IBM
commitMessage:
Customise the DbusObject paths as per IBM

Per IBM systems, the dbus paths are assumed that we
have a single system/chassis/motherboard so to align
with that, we are changing the generated object path
for ibm systems.

Signed-off-by: Manojkiran Eda <manojkiran.eda@gmail.com>
Change-Id: I2370a4dea00b85b42199d2cd569f8b284b5f2101
